quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  21,1,"∆Āadanike yim…ďe …ďen hasboore ma…ď…ďe nden, te kam…ďe hi…ďe e nder welsindaare ko …ďe …óurnii…ďe"
  21,2,Arataa e ma…ď…ďe waaju immorde ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe ko fu…ó…óaa si wanaa …ďe jentike nde hara kam…ďe hi…ďe fija
  21,3,"∆Āer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen ko welsandii…óe …ďen too√Īu…ďe suu…óa cowndi(gunndo) [wi'a] enee, hara oo wonu si wanaa …ďanndinke yeru mo'on, kaa on aray e mbilewu hara onon hi…óon sutii (ndaara)"
  21,4,"O maaki: \"Joomi am no Anndi Konngol ngol ka kammu e ka Leydi Kanko ko O Nanoowo Anndu…óo On"
  21,5,"Ko woni, …ďe wi'u: \"Ko nde jii…ďu-jaa…ďu koy…ói, toode, o fefindi nde, ko woni, kanko ko o yimoowo, awa yo o addan en Aayewal wano aran…ďe …ďen Nuliranoo non"
  21,6,"Gom…óinaali ado ma…ď…ďe immorde e saare Men halki nde. Enee, hara ko kam…ďe goom…óita"
  21,7,"Men Nulaali ado maa…óa si wanaa wor…ďe Men Wahayina e ma…ď…ďe, lanndee yim…ďe defte …ďen si tawii wonii on anndaa. @Corrected"
  21,8,"Men wa…óaali …ďe …ďalli …ďe √Īaamataa √Īaametee, …ďe laataaki kadi luttintee…ďe"
  21,9,"Refti Men Goonginani …ďe Fodoore nden Men danndi …ďe wonndude e …ďen …ďe Men Muuyi, Men halki fantin…ďe …ďen"
  21,10,Gom…óii Men jippinii faade e moo…óon Deftere no e nder mayre jaŇčtawol moo…óon. Kaa on hakkiltaa
